snippet.textDisplay:
The very first note by Humera was so spot on.. was js reading an article in a magazine and suddenly awestruck with that first note itself. Great duet. Kept the essence of the original. Nabeel's voice emotes love, peace and patience with such ease.. Thehrao kya hai awaaz main.. Pitching so controlled. CS 10's best episode so far.. Flavors of Sufism, Romance, pep, ghazal in one episode..
For Rohail Army: Aur bhi dukh hai zamaane main iske siwaaa..
